      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the doctor thing but honestly my GP is always super rushed and it's such a pain to get an appointment just for a pill change. since i'm feeling so healthy and my lifestyle hasn't changed, wouldn't my body naturally need less medication? it feels like a lot to keep taking 5mg if i'm not even feeling sick. is there any specific reason why 2mg wouldn't be a safe maintenance dose for someone in my position?",
